              "description_html": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: inherit\" data-color-scope=\"outer\"><span>一名或多名社群成員識別一項</span><strong><span>行業挑戰</span></strong><span>，並在特定</span><strong><span>專案</span></strong><span>或</span><strong><span>工作流</span></strong><span>中，以白皮書、規範或設計等形式起草貢獻。</span></span></span></p>"
